OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murder of mother-
OL,4,Cof-four Natasha Melendez
OL,6,FA 35-year-old man has been handed a
OL,7,Flife sentence after he pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto the murder of Natasha Melendez.
OL,10,FMs Melendez, who was 32 and originally
OL,11,Ffrom Venezula, was attacked on 22
OL,12,FMarch 2020 and died from her injuries
OL,13,Fon 1 April 2020.
OL,15,FAt a previous court appearance, John
OL,16,FDavid Scott denied the charges.
OL,18,FHe appeared in the dock of Belfast
OL,19,FCrown Court on Tuesday where he
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to four charges
OL,21,Fincluding murder.
