OL,6,FDefence barrister Neil Connor KC
OL,7,Faddressed Mr Justice O'Hara and asked
OL,8,Fthat his client be re-arraigned.
OL,10,FWith an address as HMP Maghaberry,
OL,11,FScott was asked to stand by a court
OL,12,Fclerk. He was then charged with
OL,13,Fmurdering Ms Melendez on 1 April, 2020.
OL,15,FWhen asked how he pleaded, Scott
OL,16,Fpaused then replied "guilty".
OL,18,FHe was also charged with, and pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to, three prior physical
OL,20,Fattacks on the mother-of-four.
