OL,6,FHe admitted causing grievous bodily
OL,7,Fharm to Ms Melendez on a date between
OL,8,FFebruary 13 and March 7, 2020,
OL,9,Fassaulting her and causing her actual
OL,10,Fbodily harm on a date between December
OL,11,F1 and December 25, 2019 and assaulting
OL,12,Fher on February 15, 2020.
OL,14,FAs Ms Melendez's mother and aunt sat
OL,15,Fin the public gallery of Court 13,
OL,16,FScott appeared emotional after
OL,17,Fentering 'guilty' pleas to all four
OL,18,Fcharges.
