OL,6,FFollowing this Mr Justice O'Hara
OL,7,Faddressed Scott as he stood in the
OL,8,Fdock and said: "As a result of the
OL,9,Ffact you have pleaded guilty to murder
OL,10,Ftoday amongst other offences, I am now
OL,11,Fpassing on you the only sentence which
OL,12,Fis permitted by law which is a Life
OL,13,FSentence."
