OL,6,FThe senior judge also told Scott that
OL,7,Fa Tariff hearing will take place "at a
OL,8,Flater stage... at which the minimum
OL,9,Fperiod you will spend in custody
OL,10,Fbefore being considered for release by
OL,11,Fthe Parole Commissioners will be
OL,12,Fdetermined, but for today's purposes I
OL,13,Fam sentencing you to Life
OL,14,FImprisonment."
OL,16,FDuring today's hearing, Mr Connor told
OL,17,FMr Justice O'Hara there were
OL,18,F"difficulties" in the case that he
OL,19,Fsaid were "created by Covid".
