OL,9,Finterviewed by police until January
OL,10,F2022.
OL,12,FMr Connor also said he would be
OL,13,Fseeking reports including a Pre-
OL,14,FSentence Report ahead of sentencing.
OL,16,FCrown barrister Rick Weir KC then told
OL,17,FMr Justice O'Hara that the prosecution
OL,18,Fwill be seeking Victim Impact
OL,19,FStatements.
